Package fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.io.parsing

Class TextGrammar

java.lang.Object
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.io.parsing.TextGrammar
public class TextGrammar extends Object
This static class defines the conventions used to save graph elements as text. For example, which delimiter for which kind of token, etc.

CAUTION: change in this file will corrupt ALL SAVED configuration files.

Author:
gignoux
